  <sect2>
    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>
      Install the package by running the following commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>make -f Makefile-libbz2_so</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>cp -v bzlib.h /usr/include &amp;&amp;
cp -av libbz2.so* /usr/lib &amp;&amp;
ln -sv libbz2.so.1.0 /usr/lib/libbz2.so</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

